EVALUATION DU PROJET D'EXPANSION DE
            LA SNMC

abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed project includes: (a)
            construction of a 500,000 tons per year cement plant at
            Saida; (b) expansion and reorganization of SNMC's
            distribution system; (c) technical assistance to the Societe
            Nationale de Comptabilite (SNC), the state enterprise
            responsible for auditing and accounting.
